sequenceDiagram
    participant Kafka as Internal Kafka Cluster<br/>9092/TCP (dev) · 9096/TCP (prod)
    participant Processor as kafka-processor<br/>Python CLI (offline)
    participant FS as Local Filesystem<br/>data/ directory
    participant Build as Container Build<br/>Dockerfile.konflux
    participant Registry as Image Registry
    participant Operator as model-registry-operator
    participant InitC as Init Container<br/>odh-model-performance-data
    participant Volume as Shared Volume<br/>/app/benchmarks
    participant Catalog as model-catalog<br/>(Model Registry)

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Kafka,FS: Flow 1: Offline Data Preparation
        Kafka->>Processor: CDC messages<br/>SASL_SSL / SCRAM-SHA-512
        Note right of Processor: Entity classification<br/>by topic name & field heuristics
        Processor->>Processor: Parse CDC envelope<br/>(modern or Debezium format)
        Processor->>Processor: Classify entity type<br/>(model, perf, eval, validation, provider, variant)
        Processor->>Processor: Apply transforms<br/>(OverallAccuracy, HardwareConfig)
        Processor->>FS: Write JSON/NDJSON files<br/>provider/model/ hierarchy
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over FS,Registry: Flow 1 (cont): Image Build
        FS->>Build: COPY data/ → /app/benchmarks
        Build->>Registry: Push image<br/>odh-model-performance-data-rhel9
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Operator,Catalog: Flow 2: Runtime Data Injection
        Operator->>Operator: Reconcile model-catalog<br/>Deployment spec
        Note right of Operator: Sets init container<br/>image reference
        InitC->>Volume: Copy /app/benchmarks<br/>to shared volume
        Note right of InitC: Init container completes<br/>and terminates
        Catalog->>Volume: Read benchmark data<br/>from shared volume
    end
